{"tid":740280,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Dse放榜  諗緊入hku 定 cu 既入一入黎","createTime":"2018-07-12T17:29:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-15T14:40:17.000Z","uid":185290,"like":14,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"77e5dd245772db9f51c38bedce6d261d36c5fbd8","tid":740280,"uid":185290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T17:29:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   hku<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  cu<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n首先，唔好講咩三大。一間冇歷史冇culture 冇medical school 冇 law, 淨係得幾個大faculty ，再請一班好高學歷既大陸人， 做好多research 出好多journal 而推砌出黎既排名，真係完全為呢個求學只是求分數既社會錦上添花。<br />\n<br />\n除非你一定要讀design, fashion and textile, communication, physiotherapy 呢啲咁就另計。否則如果你分數夠，你只會諗hku/cu.<br />\n<br />\n我地會由幾方面去研究hku 同 cu既優劣，由最重要既講起<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 女<br />\n呢個唔駛諗，hku 係完勝cu. 當然間唔中cu 都會有靚女，例如今屆候選港姐（雖然佢ig 真係好煩好自戀，m痛都要post story）。<br />\n但如果你落去hku 再去 cu行一轉，你會唔明點解大家都係叫大學站，點解質素差咁遠<br />\n<br />\n2. 地理<br />\n唔駛講啦，一個港島，一個遠過寶島<br />\n猶其係夜晚，你蒲完，仲要左轉右轉小巴，的士又唔過海<br />\n大學站落完仲要行多20分鐘先上到Shaw, 加上半夜三更，人影都冇隻<br />\nHku唔同，因為幾夜都會有班on9仔岩岩先食完宵，4點仲有得食新興<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3. 人<br />\nHku 啲人係串啲黑人憎啲，但cu 又普遍毒啲。工作上面會覺得hku啲人醒啲，但走精面，cu啲人純啲，勤力啲<br />\n<br />\n4. 食<br />\nHku canteen 應該貴過cu。如果計學校附近，hku都多啲野食。<br />\n<br />\n5. 文化<br />\nHku hall各有文化，但住得就預左俾人chur。 Cu 行college 制，可以摺啲，冇人逼你quit<br />\n<br />\n6. 眼界<br />\n呢個好緊要 新界始終係新界，cu 人可以見識既野真係會少啲，除非你自發性識好多出面既人。<br />\n<br />\n7. Sports<br />\nCu 有on99 體育堂。hku 就可以住hall揀玩lacrosse, hockey ，softball 呢啲冷門野<br />\n<br />\n8. 另類體驗<br />\n只知hku 有starr Hall 8p.<br />\nCu就得生命麵包<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bc077a1538d9999ddcc33c50c8e830dc4f47644","tid":740280,"uid":185290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T17:31:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f3d354395c0e3acc3c62b0d61a0521b3d5bf084","tid":740280,"uid":185290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T17:31:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1eb45c273b3c45928790a8cac8382fb47e34b91","tid":740280,"uid":80107,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T17:34:31.000Z","msg":"仲有得玩屌打塊面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28c6fff7cc64910799ce2f1a001d7085fc8c5daf","tid":740280,"uid":114483,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T17:34:58.000Z","msg":"樓主不如直接叫人入hku"},{"pid":"f48c45e2765df0060d7c54a458e852a2592398ac","tid":740280,"uid":185290,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28c6fff7cc64910799ce2f1a001d7085fc8c5daf","tid":740280,"uid":114483,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T17:34:58.000Z","msg":"樓主不如直接叫人入hku"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T17:56:43.000Z","msg":"我都係主觀地講一啲客觀事情出黎... Hku真係好啲"},{"pid":"a0172938a38a44148a2e4609204974340d2d683c","tid":740280,"uid":185290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1eb45c273b3c45928790a8cac8382fb47e34b91","tid":740280,"uid":80107,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T17:34:31.000Z","msg":"仲有得玩屌打塊面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T17:58:04.000Z","msg":"花生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我仲見過有人係main building 個鐘樓搞野"},{"pid":"21f762e5c778009194339514f0c998aa944fc6d2","tid":740280,"uid":116364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T18:38:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"48bac9600b054d5d322d